profile:
For over 10 years, Harmony Door Service has been servicing the southern Ontario region with professional overhead garage door sales, service and installation.

Harmony Door Service takes confidence in knowing that when we service or install your overhead door it will function as per manufactured requirements. Our friendly and professional crew is excited to help you with all of your overhead door situations.

At Harmony Door Service, we know that we are your best choice to get your garage door installed and working perfectly and efficiently. With all of our years of experience, we are confident that we have a solution for all of your door problems.
hours: Monday to Friday from 8 AM to 5 PM. 24h Emergency Service
